HEADWORD: Double-breasted
<hw>Dou"ble-breast`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Folding or
lapping over on the breast, with a row of buttons and buttonholes on
each side; <as>as, a <ex>double-breasted</ex> coat</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

